繼〈明鏡〉周刊報道了總理府曾利用默克爾訪華之機為Wirecard開展游說的消息之后，德國政府終於承認，默克爾總理曾親自在中國談及Wirecard問題。政府發言人德默爾（ Ulrike Demmer）表示：'默克爾確實曾談及這個話題。'這位發言人沒有透露當時會談的具體內容，她表示，原則上，總理府經常會利用外訪機會推介德國企業。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n直接屌東德婆奶共囉<br />\n連登仔咁都睇唔明呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b58b257d80da70ba59a913467c7b7437356718","tid":2119793,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"小報講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8f44f92dcf21112a0fa3fadf73bdb7723fb718","tid":2119793,"uid":53117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"德狗自己廢又要喺度單單打打，講到自己奶共冇問題，係英國唔on9咁<br />\n收皮啦，又唔諗吓點解自己咁冇牙力，仲話想歐洲做第三勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76913c91e3d22279a2464cbb71408f2e9d9ed94c","tid":2119793,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"東德遺物，奶共正常"},{"pid":"ee3ae63bce32bc6ec0bed041d1a7c796e13f94fa","tid":2119793,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"唔係敢唔敢<br />\n係已經畀人放咗上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b1e6886f88b32fff5213bdfe22afd7b03f8c03","tid":2119793,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8f44f92dcf21112a0fa3fadf73bdb7723fb718","tid":2119793,"uid":53117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"德狗自己廢又要喺度單單打打，講到自己奶共冇問題，係英國唔on9咁<br />\n收皮啦，又唔諗吓點解自己咁冇牙力，仲話想歐洲做第三勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"奶共得嚟又要靠美國駐軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c7f37a21fa606c67b1ac863091cc068362fcb","tid":2119793,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T10:12:48.000Z",